<div class="page-download">
	<div class="contain" >
		<div class="download-divs clearfix">
			<h4>热门下载</h4>
			<div class="download pull-left" id="download_android" ng-mouseover="setHover()" ng-mouseleave="setUnHover()">
				<img class="pull-left" alt="download_android logo" src="images/download_android.png" />
				<div class="text-contant pull-left">
					<h4>{{logoName}} for Android</h4>
					<small>最新版本：v{{android.version}}</small>
					<p><small>大小：{{android.size}}MB</small></p>
				</div>		
				<div class="download-hover  ng-class:{'hidden':!hoverAndroid}">
					<a class="hover-pannel" href="{{host}}/eas/eqiDownload?pm=android">
						<img class="center-block" alt="download_android logo" src="images/download_hover.png" >
						<h4>下载</h4>
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="download pull-left" id="download_iphone" ng-mouseover="hoverIphone=true" ng-mouseleave="hoverIphone=false">
				<img class="pull-left" alt="download_iphone logo" src="images/download_iphone.png" />
				<div class="text-contant pull-left">
					<h4>{{logoName}} for iPhone</h4>
					<small>最新版本：v{{iphone.version}}</small>
					<p><small>大小：{{iphone.size}}B</small></p>
				</div>
				<div class="download-hover  ng-class:{'hidden':!hoverIphone}">
					<a class="hover-pannel" href="{{host}}/eas/eqiDownload?pm=iphone">
						<img class="center-block" alt="download_iphone logo" src="images/download_hover.png" >
						<h4>下载</h4>
					</a>
				</div>
			</div> 
			<div class="download pull-left" id="download_windows" >
				<img class="pull-left" alt="download_windows logo" src="images/download_windows.png" />
				<div class="text-contant pull-left">
					<h4>{{logoName}} for WP</h4>				
					<small>敬请期待……</small>
					<p>&nbsp;</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="download-contant clearfix">
			<div class="pull-left" style="width:50%">
				<h4 >短信下载</h4>
			</div>
			<div  class="pull-left" style="width:50%">
				<h4 >二维码下载</h4>
			</div>	
			<div class="form-border pull-left clearfix">
				<div class="message-pannel pull-left" >
					<p>输入您的手机号，我们会发送一条短信到您的手机，点击短信中的网址即可下载{{logoName}}客户端。</p>
					<div class="message-form">
		        		<form role="form" name="downloadForm" class="form-horizontal " ng-submit="sendDownloadURL()" novalidate>  
		                	<div class="form-group">
		                    	<input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="请在此输入您的手机号" maxlength="11"  ng-model="telephone" ng-change="resetMessages()">
		                	</div>
							<div class="form-group group-verification">
		                    	<input class="pull-left form-control" placeholder="请输入验证码" maxlength="4" ng-model="captchar_code" type="text" >
		                   		<div class="pull-left code-image" ng-click="refreshCode()" title="点击刷新">
		                        	<img ng-src="code/?{{fakeRandom}}" alt="验证码图片">
		                    	</div>
		                	</div>
		                	<div class="alert alert-success ng-class:{'hidden':!Message}">{{Message}}</div>
		                	<div class="alert alert-danger ng-class:{'hidden':!errorMessage}">{{errorMessage}}</div>
		                	<button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">免费发送到手机</button>
		                </form>
	        		</div>
	       			
				</div>
				<div class="qrCode-form pull-left">
					<p>使用手机二维码软件扫描下图，即可直接下载{{logoName}}客户端。</p>
					<img class="qrCode center-block" src="images/qr_code.png"  alt="二维码图片"/>
				</div>
			</div>	
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
